HB199 Enrolled
1 Enrolled, An Act,
2 To alter, rearrange, and extend the boundary lines and
3 corporate limits of the Town of Morris in Jefferson County.
4 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA:
5 Section 1. The boundary lines and corporate limits of
6 the Town of Morris in Jefferson County are altered,
7 rearranged, and extended to include within the corporate
8 limits of the municipality, in addition to the lands now
9 included, all of the following territory:
10 BEG NW COR OF NW¼ OF SE¼ SEC 3 TP 15 SR 3W THW 235 FT
11 TH N 283.9 FT TO S/L SARDIS RD TH NELY ALG ROW 665.6 FT TH
12 SELY ALG ROW 1247.1 FT TH S 445.7 FT TH W 520 FT TH N 500 FT
13 TO POB SECT 03 TWSP 15S RANGE 3W
14 Section 2. In accordance with Section 11-42-6 of the
15 Code of Alabama 1975, a map showing the proposed territory to
16 be altered, rearranged, and extended from the Town of Morris
17 is on file and open to public inspection in the Office of the
18 Judge of Probate in Jefferson County, Alabama.
19 Section 3. This act shall become effective on October
20 1, 2026.
